              "free_text": [
                " Gamma rays were detected using 135%",
                "HPGe detector, oriented at 0deg with respect to the",
                "beam-axis, placed in close proximity to the target.",
                "The HPGe detector was surrounded by a 16-segment",
                "NaI(Tl) annulus as anticompton shield. Both counters",
                "are surrounded on five sides by 50-mm-thick plastic",
                "scintillator to suppress cosmic-ray muons"
              ]
